<p>
  <span class="nym">Luther</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>liut</i> 'people' + <span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>heri</i> 'host, army' or <span class="lang">Ancient Greek</span> <i>έλεύθερος</i> 'free'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>The name was sometimes conflated with <a class="nym" href="Lothar">Lothar</a>.</p>
  
  


